<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>2048</title>

  <%= javascript_include_tag "bind_polyfill" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "classlist_polyfill" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "animframe_polyfill" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "keyboard_input_manager" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "html_actuator" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "grid" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "tile" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "local_storage_manager" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "game_manager" %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "pre_application" %>

  <!-- <%= stylesheet_link_tag "2048" %> -->


  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="meta/apple-touch-icon.png">
  <link rel="apple-touch-startup-image" href="meta/apple-touch-startup-image-640x1096.png" media="(device-width: 320px) and (device-height: 568px) and (-webkit-device-pixel-ratio: 2)"> <!-- iPhone 5+ -->
  <link rel="apple-touch-startup-image" href="meta/apple-touch-startup-image-640x920.png"  media="(device-width: 320px) and (device-height: 480px) and (-webkit-device-pixel-ratio: 2)"> <!-- iPhone, retina -->
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
  <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">

  <meta name="HandheldFriendly" content="True">
  <meta name="MobileOptimized" content="320">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, target-densitydpi=160dpi, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no, minimal-ui">
</head>
<body style="color: #776e65">
  <div class="new-container">
    <div class="new-heading">
      <h1 class="new-title">2048</h1>
      <div class="scores-container", style="-webkit-box-sizing: content-box; 
      																			-moz-box-sizing: content-box;
      																			box-sizing: content-box;">
        <div class="score-container", style="-webkit-box-sizing: content-box; 
      																			-moz-box-sizing: content-box;
      																			box-sizing: content-box;">0</div>
        <div class="best-container", style="-webkit-box-sizing: content-box; 
      																			-moz-box-sizing: content-box;
      																			box-sizing: content-box;">0</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="above-game">
      <p class="game-intro">Join the numbers and get to the <strong>2048 tile!</strong></p>
      <a class="restart-button">New Game</a>
    </div>

    <div class="game-container">
      <div class="game-message">
        <p></p>
        <div class="lower">
	        <a class="keep-playing-button">Keep going</a>
          <a class="retry-button">Try again</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-container">
        <div class="grid-row">
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-row">
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-row">
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid-row">
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
          <div class="grid-cell"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="tile-container">

      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="game-explanation">
      <strong class="important">How to play:</strong> Use your <strong>arrow keys</strong> to move the tiles. When two tiles with the same number touch, they <strong>merge into one!</strong>
    </p>
    <hr>
    <p>
    	<strong class="important">Note:</strong> <br>A small clone of <%= link_to "2048", 'http://gabrielecirulli.github.io/2048/', :target => '_blank' %>, based on Gabriele Ciruli's <%= link_to "code", 'https://github.com/gabrielecirulli/2048', :target => '_blank' %>. <br>
    	Did a couple of minor tweaks on it and integrated it into the Ruby on Rails framework.
    </p>
    <hr>

  </div>


</body>
</html>
